text: I want to know what is poincare conjecture not who invented it

The Poincare Conjecture is a theorem about the characterization of the 3-sphere, which is the hypersphere that bounds the unit ball in four-dimensional space. It states that if a 3-manifold is locally Euclidean and simply connected, then it is homeomorphic to the 3-sphere. The conjecture was first proposed by Henri Poincare in 190
